data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bed, 2-bath home located in the highly sought-after MANSFIELD ISD!  As you step inside, you'll notice the spacious and functional layout of this home. This home has solar screens, a formal living room, a cozy gas fireplace which is the focal point of the family living room, perfect for those chilly evenings! The formal dining room is located adjacent to the kitchen, which itself boasts ample cabinetry and a breakfast nook. In the past two years, the front yard has been landscaped with fresh sod and mulch, enhancing curb appeal. A fence and a sprinkler system has been added to keep your lawn lush and green throughout the year. It is ideally situated close to shopping centers, schools, and community parks, ensuring that all your daily needs and recreational activities are within easy reach. Commuters will appreciate the quick access to both Highways 287 and 360, making travel to neighboring cities and destinations a breeze.
